Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心火燭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對炸豬排保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是炸豬排的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想制做特製涼拌豆腐和大家一起慶祝它的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:34.95,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見你  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說要回去什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續悠閒地待著就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說悠閒待著沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以給我悠閒點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那傢伙…今天生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  可以去看一下豆腐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼無論怎麼做都會壓癟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  還想做個大的給炸豬排一個驚喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要放棄還早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也想些辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  行人都那麼說的話我再試一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人  媽媽紅豆大福做太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分送給你們一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是大饞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是小鈴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以全部都吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了小鈴特別準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是把你的那份紅豆餡換成了激辣大福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:38.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我和行人大人像紅豆大福一樣一起度過甜蜜的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不想吃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實想吃到喉嚨都塞不進去的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這涼拌豆腐完成之前  我會忍耐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福不是一秒就能吃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頑固  那樣的話就讓我來你吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  吃吧  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說味道還不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是行人大人留在外面世界的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種年齡的健全男生擁有一個兩個戀人也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往的兩人互定終身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是男人離家出走遭遇海難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流到孤島在那與絕世美女相遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有喜歡的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在如此美麗的你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法偽裝自己的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你有喜歡的人  怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是罪孽多麼深重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁錮的戀 無用的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人激情燃燒的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就不能呆在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼神不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在想念戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你以前有沒有看到過那麼悲傷的行人大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓他盡情沉浸在對戀人的思念中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給生日會的邀請帖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  今天是炸豬排的生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過說起來你沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免小鈴會失落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實行人大人有留在外面的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是小鈴望塵莫及的可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過比起她還是我比較有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人為我著迷 無法抵禦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還不知道是不是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你不想承認的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也看到了吧  那行人大人有所思的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種深陷其中的眼神  不會錯一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念戀人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  不能呆在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實差不多是對故鄉產生眷戀之情的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶都那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不單是思念戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念故鄉或者家人都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是思鄉病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說男人在失落的時候能簡單地攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下你的策略了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓你搶先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到不同於平常的我的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人也是一 擊 必 殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就讓你忘記外面的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是喜歡搶先立功的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  只不過去看一下行人大人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不是打扮得漂漂亮亮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜才是  那行李是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是精心準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是凜擅長的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪異的裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓行人放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得穿上讓他覺得舒心的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很早以前就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  洋服的話我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音那洋服一百年前就過時了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落後時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是最新的流行趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃呢  化了妝變身成成熟女性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人也會超高興…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來行人也為我著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是化妝  是妖怪妝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊了 行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才女孩的照片沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和雪乃在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  難道想離開小島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道出海很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被大漩渦捲進去了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  你這笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想回到那女孩的身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是想把這個放出去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  居然奪走我的作戰方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴你真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來大家那是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是褶邊還是絲質琉璃都太落後時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那千影小姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說公子很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起來用雪乃的魅力來安慰你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來治癒行人大人內心的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人  為忘掉故鄉的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好開始新的戀情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  用我的料理打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃也給你熱情的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你忘記那個戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來讓他忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大家快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我來把戀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說戀人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說什麼戀人  究竟在說誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人所持有照片中的那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}原來叫美咲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}不對  美咲是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼戀人  完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  是誰說的給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼行人大人會有憂傷的眼神呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  剛才開始就有什麼在咕嚕咕嚕地在燒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然知道鹽鹵的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鹽鹵  在海中提取食鹽後剩下的溶液）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那「苦苦」是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「苦苦」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹽鹵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用在讓豆腐凝固方面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我家爺爺崇尚武學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種自己做蕎麥面和豆腐生活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邊看著海一直都在想為何小鈴無法做好豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然想起以前爺爺做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在想要讓豆腐凝固的鹽鹵是否不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那憂傷的眼神是在想豆腐的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  行人用認真的表情在沉思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也想讓炸豬排的生日會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就快完成豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能一起幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}桃和笹身一整天都和小豬排玩的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一會了 加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼著急的回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉阿開們也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為了慶祝炸豬排的生日而聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人什麼時候來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不來幫忙只有在吃的時候出現還真是不吃虧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排兩歲了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才兩根蠟燭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許願時如果能把火吹滅的話願望就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  請吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我自己會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  嫁不出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:27.97,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}「好害羞  玩偶裝」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排那麼高興太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  信呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}今天是美咲的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好在生日那天要陪她去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法實現約定  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著至少把信寄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  其實你想回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是炸豬排的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從來到這個島上受到許多炸豬排的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丟下那麼拼命的小鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在就把信寄出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魚片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為小瓶的話應該能穿過大漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎  無論怎麼扔都會被沖回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:22:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了小鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小鈴
